    "patch_code": "public String format(Date date) {\n    long time = date.getTime();\n    long julianDayNumber = ((long)(time / NUM_DAYS_MS)) + 2440587;\n    \n    int z = (int)(julianDayNumber - mZeroDay);\n    int woy;\n    \n    if(z < numDaysInFirstWeek){\n        if((numDaysInFirstWeek+mMinimalDaysInFirstWeek-1 <= mNumDaysBeforeFirstJan1970 ) &&\n            ( mNumDaysBeforeFirstJan1970 < numDaysInFirstWeek)){\n           // do nothing\n        }else{\n            return Integer.toString(z);            \n        } \n    }\n        \n    woy = (z < 0 ? z : ((z - numDaysBetweenStartAndPrevMonday) / numDaysPerWeek));\n    \n    return Integer.toString(woy + 1);      \n}",
